      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This car is in good, solid condition and has been well-loved and reliably maintained. It drives smoothly, looks great on the road, and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner who appreciates a well-cared-for ride!",
