      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This specimen remains in pristine, showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of fastidious care. For the discerning enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection, this offering represents the definitive choice in its class.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
